  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "テトリスとシューティングゲームが融合した「ランパート」は、戦略と砲撃アクションを組み合わせたゲームです。テトリススタイルのパーツで城を築き、砲台を配置し、敵を bombard（爆撃）し、修理を試み、再びすべてを繰り返します。オリジナルのアーケード版にはシングルプレイヤーとツープレイヤーモードがあり、後の改訂版ではスリープレイヤーのゲームプレイも追加されています。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Rampart may refer to:\n\nRampart (fortification), a defensive wall or bank around a castle, fort or settlement\nRampart may also refer to:\n\nLAPD Rampart Division, a division of the Los Angeles Police Department\nRampart scandal, a blanket term for the widespread corruption of the Rampart Division\nRamparts (magazine), a leftist American magazine that was published from 1962 through 1975\nRampart Search and Rescue, Adams County, Colorado\nRampART Social Center, an anti-authoritarian social centre in Whitechapel, East London UK\nRampart High School, a National School of Excellence in Colorado Springs, Colorado\nRamparts (Lille Gate) Commonwealth War Graves Commission Cemetery in the Ypres Salient, Belgium\nRAMPART-A, a secret signals intelligence program led by the United States National Security Agency",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    }
  ],
  "first_release_date": "1992-10-30",
